FBIS4-1772 "drchi064_n_94002" FBIS-CHI-94-064 Daily Report 4 Mar 1994 Economic & Agricultural Li Peng Promulgates Medical Institutions Managing Rules Li Peng Promulgates Medical Institutions Managing Rules OW0204095094 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0634 GMT 4 Mar 94 OW0204095094 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service Chinese BFN [Text] Beijing, 4 Mar (XINHUA) -- Decree No. 149 of the People's Republic of China State Council: The "Regulations for Managing Medical Institutions" is hereby promulgated for enforcement beginning on 1 September 1994. [Signed] Premier Li Peng [Dated] 26 February 1994
